			<h1>6 steps to creating a successful Facebook ad</h1>

            	
<div class="postauthor">
            
            		<p>Posted by <a href="http://www.freedomlovin.com/author/kevin/" title="Posts by Kevin" rel="author">Kevin</a> on Wednesday, March 5, 2014 &middot; <a href="http://www.freedomlovin.com/6-steps-to-creating-a-successful-facebook-ad/#comments"><span data-lf-article-id="1266" data-lf-site-id="339441" class="livefyre-commentcount">2 Comments</span></a>&nbsp;</p>
                    
                </div>
             

			<div id="ssbartop"></div>
<div class="scrollbarbox" id="scrollbarbox">
<table class="tssbar" align="center" width="60" cellspacing="1" border="0">
<tr>
<td align="center" >
<div style="height:64px;width:48px;margin:0pt auto;" class="sharebarbtn sbarfblike"><iframe src="http://www.facebook.com/plugins/like.php?app_id=126788060742161&amp;href=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.freedomlovin.com%2F6-steps-to-creating-a-successful-facebook-ad%2F&amp;send=false&amp;layout=box_count&amp;width=48&amp;show_faces=false&amp;action=like&amp;colorscheme=light&amp;font&amp;height=64" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" style="border:none; overflow:hidden; width:48px; height:64px;" allowTransparency="true"></iframe></div>
</td>
